local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["vivisection"]={"vivisection","[vɪvɪ'sekʃ(ə)n]","[,vɪvɪ'sɛkʃən]","n.活体解剖",'n.活体解剖','Many animal rights groups oppose vivisection on the grounds that it is inhumane to the animals involved.','许多动物权益组织反对活体解剖，因为这对于对被解剖的动物来说太不人道了。','I believe I am not interested to know whether vivisection produces results that are profitable to the human race or doesn\'t.','活体解剖是否对人类有益，这一点我没有兴趣去了解。即使我知道它对人类有益，也不会改变我对它的敌意。'}
